(ad_X)^m(Y) = \sum_{k=0}^m \binom{m}{k} X^kY(-X)^{m-k}
(ad_X)^m(Y)=[X,\ldots,[X,[X,Y]]\cdots].
e^{ad_X}(Y) = \sum_{p=0}^\infty \frac{(ad_X)^p(Y)}{p!}
e^{ad_X}(Y) = \sum_{p=0}^\infty \sum_{k=0}^p \binom{p}{k} \frac{1}{p!} X^kY(-X)^{p-k}
e^X Y e^{-X}
L_X(A)=XA
R_X(A)=AX
ad_X(A)=XA-AX=L_X(A)-R_X(A)=(L_X-R_X)(A)
e^{ad_X}=e^{L_X-R_X}=e^{L_X}e^{-R_X}
e^{U+V}=e^Ue^V
